                  </hi>. I am a cow-keeper, and keep vans and carts. The prisoner was driver of my vans for nine or ten days—I paid him 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. a week and his board—on the 13th of December I gave him 34<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. to go to the Vauxhall gas-work for two chaldrons of coke—I said I did not know ex<lb></lb>actly how much it would be—I never saw him again till that day month, and then took him—I never got my money back—he sent the van home empty by a little boy.</p>
